{"data":[{"date":"12:45 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atletico Madrid vs Inter Milan 02h05 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-atletico-madrid-vs-inter-milan-02h05-ngay-128-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Atletico Madrid vs Inter Milan l\u00fac 02h05 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atletico Madrid vs Inter Milan 02h05 ng\u00e0y 128 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atletico Madrid vs Inter Milan 02h05 ng\u00e0y 128 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Atletico-vs-Inter-Milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Atletico Madrid vs Inter Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Atletico Madrid vs Inter Milan: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>D\u00f9 c\u00f3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luka Modric hay kh\u00f4ng, Inter v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u00f9a H\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, khi \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u1edfi th\u1ebf, ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u00eam nay kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n t\u1ea1i Champions League, th\u00ec s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i n\u01a1i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 khi b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a Nerazzurri \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Atletico s\u1ebd bay \u0111i Estonia \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Real Madrid v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Diego Simeone \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, khi h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Cagliari. D\u00f9 ch\u01b0a d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Atletico \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo \u0111\u00fang phong c\u00e1ch s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady so v\u1edbi Inter, Atletico ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng. Inter ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1c v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1eeb Miranda (Brazil), Marcelo Brozovic v\u00e0 Ivan Perisic (Croatia), nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf CLB. M\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng Mauro Icardi, Radja Nainggolan, Milan Skriniar, Stefan de Vrij hay Antonio Candreva \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a World Cup v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau. K\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 H\u00e8 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd k\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1edbm, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Inter th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2017, Inter c\u00f2n c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Internation Champions Cup v\u00e0 giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Villarreal, Betis, Lyon, Bayern v\u00e0 Chelsea. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5y khi\u1ebfn Inter kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecb \u201ckh\u1edbp\u201d v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Wanda Metropolitano \u0111\u00eam nay, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u00e1o xanh-\u0111en v\u1ed1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t \u1edf nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nAtletico r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u201cb\u1eaft n\u1ea1t\u201d nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Barca hay Bayern, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 \u201c\u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb\u201d nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e1 \u201cc\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi\u201d nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd. Inter v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i l\u00ean b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t quan tr\u1ecdng cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Simeone.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Inter c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico c\u1ee7a c\u1ed1 nh\u00e2n Simeone \u0111\u00eam nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\n- Atletico: \u0110\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <br>\r\n- Inter: V\u1eafng Nainggolan (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng). <br>\r\n- Theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Atletico th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 2, thua 2/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y; th\u1eafng 3, thua 4/7 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. <br>\r\n- Theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Inter th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 1, thua 3/7 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua; th\u1eafng 3, thua 2/5 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 b\u00e0n: 3/4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Atletico v\u00e0 4/5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Inter \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00f4i b\u00ean c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u00eam nay s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5366","checkdouble":"194251"},{"date":"13:53 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs AC Milan 02h00 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-ac-milan-02h00-ngay-128-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid vs AC Milan l\u00fac 02h00 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 Bernabeu Trophy 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs AC Milan 02h00 ng\u00e0y 128 Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs AC Milan 02h00 ng\u00e0y 128 Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Real-Madrid-vs-AC-Milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real Madrid vs AC Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Real Madrid vs AC Milan: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup 2018 thua Man United 1-2, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng li\u1ec1n 2 tr\u1eadn sau \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Julen Lopetegui \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo (sang Juventus). Nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ecd. \u1ede c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 Roma, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u1eabn v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Marco Asensio v\u00e0 Gareth Bale.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Trong 11 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u1edf Bernabeu, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn, h\u00f2a 3, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1 l\u1ea7n. Do v\u1eady, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Milan, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ec7. \u1ede 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Milan ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 1 v\u00e0 th\u1eafng 2. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, Milan \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Barca (\u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Real Madrid) v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo v\u1eady, c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin c\u00fap s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00eam nay!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nCh\u1eb5n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng<br>\r\n4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ch\u1eb5n. 6/9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Real Madrid ch\u1eb5n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. 5/7 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Miilan x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Do v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00eam nay nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ch\u1eb5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5365","checkdouble":"194252"},{"date":"15:41 11/08","title":"Mourinho l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khi Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh nhau penalty","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-len-tieng-khi-pogba-va-sanchez-tranh-nhau-penalty.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau khi hai ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tranh nhau qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Paul Pogba cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ecbn v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh anh m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0 gi\u1edd ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cho Man Utd.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i, Alexis Sanchez c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi b\u1ecb tranh gi\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi anh r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi su\u00f4n s\u1ebb sau n\u1eeda n\u0103m kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 \u1edf Old Trafford. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao Chile \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u00f3 khi s\u00fat b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang tay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Leicester trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/mourinho-len-tieng-khi-pogba-va-sanchez-tranh-nhau-penalty.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh \u0111\u00e1 penalty \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec gi\u1eefa anh v\u00e0 Sanchez. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus c\u00f3 n\u00f3i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh ri\u00eang m\u1ed9t ai \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch s\u00fat penalty c\u1ea3, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 HLV c\u0169ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nhau ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n can thi\u1ec7p. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u01b0\u1eddng cho Alexis v\u00ec n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Man Utd m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ti\u1ebfp l\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh, HLV Jose Mourinho c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19: \u201cPaul s\u00fat penalty r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 hai v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ba \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p thi\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 tin v\u00ec m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean Paul gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea5m 11m. Sau c\u00f9ng th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018 c\u01a1 m\u00e0. Nh\u00ecn m\u00e0 xem, Kasper Schmeichel b\u1eaft ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ra sao v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5364","checkdouble":"194260"},{"date":"15:38 11/08","title":"Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e2n binh MU sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Leicester","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/pogba-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-fred-sau-tran-thang-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pogba \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn v\u00e0o t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Man United.</h2><h2>Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Fred</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt ng\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng Pogba \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester \u0111\u00eam qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m penalty ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Luke Shaw ph\u00fat 83 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh v\u00e0 Fred c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u1eefa anh v\u00e0 Fred.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Fred sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Fred sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/pogba-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-fred-sau-tran-thang-leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Fred sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y Fred l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Pereira d\u00f9 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng th\u00fa th\u1eadt l\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi c\u00f3 Fred c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m vui h\u01a1n khi c\u00f3 Fred trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Pogba ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c tranh c\u00e3i v\u1edbi Sanchez</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n penalty. Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1 penalty nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb Pogba t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y: <em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e3nh tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1 penalty. M\u00e0 d\u00f9 HLV c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng cho nhau. H\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n penalty. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3 cho Sanchez. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVideo t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester:<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester-172-194247.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-21-cua-mu-truoc-leicester-172-194222.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5363","checkdouble":"194261"},{"date":"16:02 11/08","title":"HLV Sarri k\u00eau g\u1ecdi C\u0110V Chelsea ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/hlv-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Chelsea. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. \u00d4ng c\u00f9ng Chelsea thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c, kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Community Shield c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 59 tu\u1ed5i thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp cho The Blues \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7, Sarri m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV Chelsea sau khi h\u1ecd sa th\u1ea3i Antonio Conte. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng cho m\u00f9a m\u1edbi b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea s\u1eafp t\u1edbi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi Conte v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m quen.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/hlv-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sarri l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Chelsea. \u00d4ng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng CLB. Sarri c\u0169ng l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb C\u0110V v\u00e0 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1ea5t r\u00f5\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng trong n\u1eeda sau c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1. T\u00f4i d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-21h00-ngay-118-nhay-mua-cung-sarriball-172-194230.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-21h00-ngay-118-nhay-mua-cung-sarriball.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-21h00-ngay-118-nhay-mua-cung-sarriball-172-194230.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea (21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8): Nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa c\u00f9ng Sarriball</span><br>\r\n<span>Tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Conte \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Sarri. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2017/18.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec9nh ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng (\u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 5 Premier League). V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u1edf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec9nh ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh trong 1 ho\u1eb7c 2 th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cL\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n ch\u1edd th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mang l\u1ea1i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-cau-thu-sap-roi-chelsea-172-194238.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/aubameyang-172-194218.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-chelsea-len-tieng-xac-nhan-tuong-lai-cua-hazard-172-194216.html\">HLV Chelsea l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-ung-ho-chelsea-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-the-gioi-vi-thu-mon-kepa-172-194215.html\">Pep Guardiola \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Chelsea vung ti\u1ec1n v\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ai-o-real-madrid-da-khuyen-kovacic-ra-di-cap-ben-chelsea-172-194208.html\">Ai \u1edf Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 khuy\u00ean Kovacic ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5362","checkdouble":"194262"},{"date":"16:29 11/08","title":"HLV Leicester: \u201cTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/hlv-claude-puel-phat-bieu-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U th\u1eafng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt Leicester</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. H\u1ecd m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 do c\u00f4ng Paul Pogba t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Leicester l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m. Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David De Gea m\u1edbi gi\u00fap M.U tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. \u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 83, Luke Shaw nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t, khi\u1ebfn b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 ph\u00fat 90+2 c\u1ee7a Jamie Vardy kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Claude-Puel-phat-bieu-sau-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Puel b\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Vardy kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Claude Puel h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U, n\u01a1i c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh James Maddison, Ricardo Pereira v\u00e0 Rachid Ghezzal c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ra m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c\u201d, Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester. \u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa ngay.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Puel cua Leicester\" title=\"HLV Puel cua Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/hlv-claude-puel-phat-bieu-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong hi\u1ec7p 1, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ta nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, sau khi th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ebd tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sang h\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00e1c. Sau c\u00f9ng, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPuel ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201c\u0110\u00f4i khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0y d\u00f9 s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-tran-mu-21-leicester-bong-dang-sieu-doi-truong-xuat-hien-172-194228.html\">M.U 2-1 Leicester: B\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng \u201cSi\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester-172-194247.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\">Mourinho g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: \u201cPogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i th\u00fa\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/danh-bai-leicester-mourinho-ca-ngoi-suc-manh-tap-the-cua-mu-172-194223.html\">\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester, Mourinho ca ng\u1ee3i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-21-cua-mu-truoc-leicester-172-194222.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5361","checkdouble":"194263"},{"date":"17:29 11/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Huddersfield vs Chelsea 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (Premier League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Huddersfield vs Chelsea: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea gi\u1ea3i Premier League Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh NHA 2018/19 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 11/8.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Huddersfield vs Chelsea: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea gi\u1ea3i Premier League Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh NHA 2018/19 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 11/8.</h2></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5360","checkdouble":"194264"},{"date":"11:22 11/08","title":"Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Arsenal, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1eafp c\u00f3 sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/khong-phai-arsenal-day-moi-la-doi-bong-sap-co-dembele.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Ousmane Dembele c\u1ee7a Barca, theo Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Dembele</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/khong-phai-arsenal-day-moi-la-doi-bong-sap-co-dembele.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/dembele-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-arsenal-184-194031.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele</span>, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a c\u00f3 k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Tuy nhi\u00ean, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal, phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Ousmane Dembele c\u1ee7a Barca, theo Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ousmane Dembele co the roi Camp Nou neu Barca mua Willian\" title=\"Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou n\u1ebfu Barca mua Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/arsenal-tung-chieu-doc-so-huu-dembele-khien-barca-nga-ngua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p lo ng\u1ea1i Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe s\u1ebd ra \u0111i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Thomas Tuchel tin r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng PSG, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed s\u1ebd t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng PSG chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Dembele \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca h\u01a1n l\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn PSG \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho b\u1ed9 ba Mbappe, Cavani v\u00e0 Neymar. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u0169ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5359","checkdouble":"194246"},{"date":"10:19 11/08","title":"HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Real?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-sau-khi-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u1edbi Bernabeu c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed phong \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Petr Cech ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-sau-khi-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Thibaut Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Courtois l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn anh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bernabeu thi \u0111\u1ea5u, anh mu\u1ed1n g\u1ea7n g\u0169i c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Courtois \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real, The Blues thu v\u1ec1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-194131.html\" target=\"_blank\">Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span>, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Bernabeu kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n. L\u00fd do l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i t\u1edbi Los Blancos l\u00e0 v\u00ec gia \u0111\u00ecnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf g\u1ea7n c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1ee7a Courtois?</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u1edbi Bernabeu c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri\" title=\"Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhan-dinh-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-vong-1-Premier-League-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 l\u1eafm. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Real Madrid. D\u00f9 sao c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Chelsea, t\u00f4i ch\u00fac c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Eden Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Chelsea. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn 4 l\u1ea7n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi Kepa c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Courtois hay kh\u00f4ng, HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 23 tu\u1ed5i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Kepa s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng do Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Mateo Kovacic \u00f4ng chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u1edbi Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5358","checkdouble":"194240"},{"date":"09:13 11/08","title":"Klopp v\u1eabn cay c\u00fa v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ramos l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/klopp-van-cay-cu-va-khang-dinh-ramos-la-noi-si-nhuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>G\u1ea7n 3 th\u00e1ng sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, n\u1ed7i \u0111au v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngu\u00f4i ngoai v\u1edbi Liverpool. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Klopp ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ramos v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eadt v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKlopp ch\u01b0a bu\u00f4ng tha k\u1ebb th\u00f9<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Salah nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f2n ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Sergio Ramos h\u1ea1 \u0111o v\u00e1n, v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng vai ch\u1ec9 sau 30 ph\u00fat b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, HLV Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a qu\u00ean m\u1ed1i th\u00f9 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd kh\u00f3 nghe. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ee7 \u0111o\u1ea1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i danh hi\u1ec7u d\u00f9 b\u1ecb s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c th\u1ebf n\u00e0o ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mong \u0111\u1ee3i g\u00ec \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Ramos s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu ta suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ramos v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi x\u1ea5u ch\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1\" title=\"Ramos v\u1eadt Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/klopp-van-cay-cu-va-khang-dinh-ramos-la-noi-si-nhuc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ramos v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi x\u1ea5u ch\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb h\u1ea1 \u0111o v\u00e1n trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9, l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 xa khung th\u00e0nh. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p d\u00e0nh cho con c\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u1ecdi th\u1ee7 \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng &ndash; c\u00f3 l\u1ebd t\u00f4i s\u1ebd vui l\u00f2ng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5t n\u00e0y sau 40 n\u0103m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i? Kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng trong su\u1ed1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u00fang ta n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Ramos, h\u00e3y nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 &ndash; khi c\u1eadu ta \u0103n v\u1ea1 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Juan Cuadrado nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf. Real Madrid x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, ch\u1eb3ng ai nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea9n th\u1ec9u nh\u01b0 Ramos?&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Klopp ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ramos v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd anh c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Klopp. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Ramos c\u0169ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng cho Karius, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: &quot;G\u00ec n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn Firmino c\u1ea3m l\u1ea1nh ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng?&quot;&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/thu-mon-karius-bi-roi-loan-thi-giac-sau-cu-giat-cui-cho-cua-ramos-188-187809.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/thu-mon-karius-bi-roi-loan-thi-giac-sau-cu-giat-cui-cho-cua-ramos.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/thu-mon-karius-bi-roi-loan-thi-giac-sau-cu-giat-cui-cho-cua-ramos-188-187809.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Karius b\u1ecb r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n th\u1ecb gi\u00e1c sau c\u00fa gi\u1eadt c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Ramos</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Liverpool ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7n ki\u1ec3m tra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe sau khi h\u1ee9ng tr\u1ecdn pha x\u1ea5u ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00ean ph\u00eda Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/lien-doan-judo-chau-au-ramos-ha-guc-salah-bang-ky-thuat-cam-188-187251.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/lien-doan-judo-chau-au-ramos-ha-guc-salah-bang-ky-thuat-cam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/lien-doan-judo-chau-au-ramos-ha-guc-salah-bang-ky-thuat-cam-188-187251.html\">Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Judo ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: Ramos h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Salah b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ea5m</span><br>\r\nLi\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Judo ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u1eadn ra s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u1edf pha tranh ch\u1ea5p gi\u1eefa Ramos v\u00e0 Salah v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n th\u1ebf b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m trong thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5357","checkdouble":"194241"},{"date":"11:01 11/08","title":"HLV Emery khi\u1ebfn NHM Arsenal bu\u1ed3n vui l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/hlv-emery-khien-nhm-arsenal-buon-vui-lan-lon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e1o tin vui t\u1eeb Ramsey song kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Arsenal s\u1eafp gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ramsey</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aaron Ramsey v\u1edbi Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aaron Ramsey\" title=\"Aaron Ramsey\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Unai-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Aaron Ramsey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chi-40-trieu-bang-chelsea-quyet-tam-mua-bang-duoc-sao-khung-arsenal-172-193778.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ramsey</span>, Real v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e1o tin vui t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i: &ldquo;Vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Arsenal<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ramsey, HLV Unai Emery c\u00f2n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ospina bat chinh truoc Atletico Madrid\" title=\"Ospina b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/Unai-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ospina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Carl Jenkinson, David Ospina v\u00e0 Joel Campbell c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. C\u00f2n vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n hay b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a BL\u0110&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Emery c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Emile Smith Rowe v\u00e0 Eddie Nketiah s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Man City trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5356","checkdouble":"194244"},{"date":"11:08 11/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1eafp chia tay Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/7/them-mot-tien-dao-sap-chia-tay-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t hay kh\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fenerbahce h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Origi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-southampton-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tien-dao-cua-liverpool-172-194142.html\" target=\"_blank\">Danny Ings t\u1edbi Southampton</span> theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, song c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Divock Origi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/26/Fenerbahce-muon-dua-Divock-Origi-roi-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Divock Origi mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Firmino, Sturridge v\u00e0 Solanke, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1995 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Origi, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Watford, Crystal Palace hay Wolves, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Liverpool y\u00eau c\u1ea7u khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t hay kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Origi t\u1edbi Fenerbahce l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n HLV Klopp c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Origi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Fenerbahce c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 Liverpool v\u00e0 Origi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Origi\" title=\"Origi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/29/sao-xit-liverpool-doi-lenh-klopp-de-ra-di.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Origi s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Origi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec The Kop c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTTCN H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua, song nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Origi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, Liverpool s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Klopp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5355","checkdouble":"194245"},{"date":"10:38 11/08","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 \u00fd, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. \r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Paul Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaul Pogba m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng M.U, song anh \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng. S\u1ed1 6 \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf vai tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho M.U ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m khi\u1ebfn Kasper Schmeichel ph\u1ea3i b\u00f3 tay. Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong 11 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng M.U to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, san b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Ryan Babel.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a M.U, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec1u qua ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 91 l\u1ea7n, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 68 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 54 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, 6 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, 2 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, 2 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 2 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Pogba, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f2n v\u1edbi Pogba, anh chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n cho CLB, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng M.U chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: HLV Claude Puel</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, HLV Claude Puel t\u1ef1 tin tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1: &ldquo;Leicester \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. L\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, song Leicester \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Claude Puel phat bieu ve tran MU 2-1 Leicester\" title=\"Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/hlv-claude-puel-giai-thich-ly-do-tai-sao-leicester-that-bai-truoc-mu.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Claude Puel kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t h\u00f9ng h\u1ed3n, song Leicester c\u1ee7a Claude Puel ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a M.U. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vardy ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeicester ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U. 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua (3 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 5 thua). \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Leicester \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 8 trong 9 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gh\u00e9 th\u0103m s\u00e2n Old Trafford (h\u00f2a 1).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Luke Shaw</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 Ashley Young v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau World Cup 2018, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Luke Shaw ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-leicester-tran-dau-vong-1-premier-league-201819-372-194203.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU vs Leicester </span>v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luke Shaw ghi ban dau tien cho M.U\" title=\"Luke Shaw ghi ban dau tien cho M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/luke-shaw-noi-gi-sau-khi-ghi-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luke Shaw c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng. C\u1ef1u sao Southampton l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t (99) v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n nh\u1ea5t (67) b\u00ean ph\u00eda Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuke Shaw c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, anh khi\u1ebfn Ricardo Pereira b\u00ean ph\u00eda Leicester kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, Shaw c\u00f2n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00e1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho M.U sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 67 cho h\u1ecd tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Shaw \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, Shaw x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Wes Morgan</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Wes Morgan \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ng\u00f4i sao 34 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c khi\u1ebfn Morgan kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wes Morgan co mot tran dau that vong\" title=\"Wes Morgan c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/morgan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wes Morgan c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi M.U, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1984 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, anh t\u1ecf ra ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Morgan \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb Sanchez lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe s\u1eafc l\u1eb9m, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady anh c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Harry Maguire.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Morgan \u1edf Old Trafford l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. Anh ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMorgan l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed3i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Leicester trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi M.U, n\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Jonny Evans.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Jose Mourinho</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U, \u00f4ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1. Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester khi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a M.U m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau World Cup 2018, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 6 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n&nbsp;th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho tran M.U vs Leicester\" title=\"Mourinho tran M.U vs Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/danh-bai-leicester-mourinho-ca-ngoi-suc-manh-tap-the-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho c\u00f9ng MU c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1ee7a v\u00e2y, song Mourinho v\u1eabn gi\u00fap M.U c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Old Trafford v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 55 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp trung trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Jose Mourinho b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 18 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV (th\u1eafng 11, h\u00f2a 7), ri\u00eang t\u1ea1i Premier League, &ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t&rdquo; th\u1eafng 9 trong s\u1ed1 10 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n (h\u00f2a 1).&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean d\u1eb7n d\u00f2 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c M.U ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Alexis Sanchez</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alexis Sanchez l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 cho M.U qu\u1ea3 11m ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 Paul Pogba th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ngo\u00e0i ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra 3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez de mat bong qua nhieu truoc Leicester\" title=\"Sanchez \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/sanchez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sanchez \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t sung s\u1ee9c, nh\u01b0ng Sanchez kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 ch\u1ec9 tung ra duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, Sanchez g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung v\u1edbi Rashford v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Sanchez c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u00e3 23 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Mourinho ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Sanchez ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn NHM Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: David de Gea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David de Gea v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea MU\" title=\"De Gea MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/de-gea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Gea ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Leicester, De Gea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ph\u00fat 28, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ef1c nhanh sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Maddison, t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 75 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 De Gea ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Gray.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, trong hi\u1ec7p 1 De Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ee9u thua nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n anh l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018. Trong 90 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5354","checkdouble":"194247"}]}